Product Description: WSI Pride Plus Amprolium Crumble 1.25%, packaged in a 50 lb. bag.  The Product code/number is 104636.  Tag is tan in color; with the lot number and product number located at the bottom of the tag just above the tag sew line.      The product is labeled in parts: "***WSI Pride Plus Amprolium Crumble 1.25%***For Beef and Dairy Calves***MEDICATED An aid in the prevention and treatment of coccidiosis caused by Eimeria bovis and E. zurnii in calves***ACTIVE DRUG INGREDIENT***Amprolium (Corid) 1.25%***MANUFACTURED BY WESTERN STOCKMEN'S, CALDWELL, ID 83605*** 208-459-0777***".
Reason for Recall: WSI Pride-Plus Amprolium Crumble 1.25% was found to be sub-potent for Amprolium.   The sample was detected of 0.9758% instead of 1.25% concentration of Amprolium.
Code Info: Lot No. 340209114-090712           The lot number consists of the first 9 digits, i.e., 340209114 and is a unique identifier.   The Product code is the unique code assigned in the firm's database for this named finished feed product.    The number 090712 is September 7, 2012.  The tag was made on Sept. 7. This date does not reflect the actual date of manufacture necessarily, as tags are produced at the time an order is placed. In this case, the order was placed on Sept. 7th and at that time the tags were made.
